<item>
            <title>[FELIX-1608] non-existent OBR repository is fatal</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1608</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If sigil-repos.properties references an non-existent repository, the build fails.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be better if this behaviour could be controlled by adding an extra key to each repository definition,&lt;br/&gt;
e.g. optional = true, would treat a non-existent repository as optiona&lt;/p&gt;</description>
