                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12756594" author="db82407" created="Thu, 17 Sep 2009 15:43:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;added &apos;optional&apos; attribute to OBR repos, to avoid fatal error if they don&apos;t exist.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;bld-shared;provider:    obr&lt;br/&gt;
bld-shared;level:       2&lt;br/&gt;
bld-shared;auth:        ${.}/sigil-auth.propetries&lt;br/&gt;
bld-shared;url:           &lt;a href=&quot;file:$&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;file:$&lt;/a&gt;{..}/build/repo-shared/repository.obr&lt;br/&gt;
bld-shared;optional:    true&lt;br/&gt;
bld-shared;index:       ${..}/build/bld-shared.obr&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
